{"tid":1087372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國2架殲11戰機昨越台海中線 柯Ｐ：去問韓國瑜","createTime":"2019-04-01T10:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T11:42:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c96aa1689761dc2d66657094237fe1a926a0531","tid":1087372,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"中共2架殲11戰機昨越台海中線 柯Ｐ：去問韓國瑜<br />\n<br />\n中共空軍作兩架殲11戰鬥機，在澎湖西南方空域，飛越被視為兩岸「楚河漢界」的海峽中線，儘管國軍緊急派戰機攔截，但共機卻未立刻離開，越界時間長達十分鐘，中共戰機此舉也被視為刻意挑釁台灣。不過由於高雄市長韓國瑜才剛訪中回台，如今共機卻主動挑釁，外界認為這似乎是在打臉韓國瑜。<br />\n<br />\n對此，台北市長柯文哲今受訪時，被問到共機越過海峽中線一事，不願多談，僅說「你應該去問韓國瑜，怎麼來問我」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/3730564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F3730564&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQixVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=068707cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/3730564</a>"},{"pid":"ac1b2667f1611a85fbb8a975a276e5f5d1425f0d","tid":1087372,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817cb28eba6e257f0c6e77952e275f10bad8cdc9","tid":1087372,"uid":2994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6745b43c16a178184249da60de8f2c576c154e0","tid":1087372,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"不敢惹中國？共機越線犯眾怒！韓國瑜：我滿腦在想芭樂銷售<br />\n<br />\n2019/04/01<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=520554&amp;fbclid=IwAR1cPblmWr9UM-_rZKehg0IpYwKVADOUcJUKfaVqIou3EFmUV8Tm5J40zlk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D520554%26fbclid%3DIwAR1cPblmWr9UM-_rZKehg0IpYwKVADOUcJUKfaVqIou3EFmUV8Tm5J40zlk&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQixVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=1cc93872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/fra